Money Stuff =0A A lot of problems in finance come from fire sales and conta=
gion, and a lot of =0Aregulation is organized around preventing them. Most =
classical =0A=0A=0A =0A<https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/authors/ARbTQlRLR=
